  m_text: A flicker of confusion dances in your mind as you struggle to recall even
    the simplest details of your past. Faces, names, and personal history elude you,
    leaving a void where memories once thrived. The room feels both sterile and foreboding,
    adorned with futuristic screens and blinking lights that offer no clues to your
    identity.
